<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../664/1704664.xml">
Edward Bond</link></dramatist>
</writer>
</causal_agent>
</person>
</communicator>
</physical_entity>
's <it><link>
Olly's Prison</link></it> (1993). Hill was also a character in the movie Scorpion King , in which he was a scientist and inventor. He has also played a small role in the film the Ghost and the darkness he played the dr.</p>
<p>

In addition to TV roles, Hill appeared on stage in both <it><dramatic_composition wordnetid="107007684" confidence="0.8">
<play wordnetid="107007945" confidence="0.8">
<written_communication wordnetid="106349220" confidence="0.8">
