Macbeth</link></it> (Leicester Haymarket Theatre, 1986). He played the coroner Madgett in <film_director wordnetid="110088200" confidence="0.9173553029164789">
<person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../452/55452.xml">
