<p>

Hill was cast in the role of King <link>
Théoden</link> of <site wordnetid="108651247" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../469/63469.xml">
Rohan</link></site>
 in the second and third of <film_director wordnetid="110088200" confidence="0.9173553029164789">
<screenwriter wordnetid="110564400" confidence="0.9173553029164789">
<film_maker wordnetid="110088390" confidence="0.9173553029164789">
