</fictional_character>
. When he was due to leave the set at the end of production, Peter Jackson gave Hill two gifts, Théoden's helmet and sword <artifact wordnetid="100021939" confidence="0.8">
<instrumentality wordnetid="103575240" confidence="0.8">
